text: Stéphanie Colvey (born 1949) is a Canadian photographer. Her work is included in the collections of the Musée national des beaux-arts du Québec, and the National Gallery of Canada ==References== Category:Living people Category:1949 births Category:20th-century Canadian women artists Category:21st-century Canadian women artists Category:20th-century Canadian photographers Category:21st-century Canadian photographers Category:Artists from Montreal
